      "span_text": "For example, bladder preservation for muscle-invasive bladder cancer using aggressive TURBT, chemotherapy, and external beam radiation therapy is a costly upfront investment in terms of time and money, and many would rightly ask if this investment is worth the long-term improvements in health gained [CITATION_1] ."
